snippet.title: Ryan Zehm
snippet.description: Ryan Zehm is a follower of Jesus Christ, anti-masonic activist, flat earther, philosopher, historian, antiquarian, and game developer. His original channel, Spill The Truth, was deleted by YouTube. Ryan is expanding from YouTube and is in the early stages of launching a publishing company for topics such as flat earth and hidden history. Learn more at https://beyondthepoles.com/ .
